        <description><![CDATA[
            <p><a href="https://packages.debian.org/bookworm/sq-keyring-linter" class="inline-onebox">Debian -- Details of package sq-keyring-linter in bookworm</a> not available in trixie, sid but that’s okay.</p>
<p>Quote <a href="https://tracker.debian.org/news/1636301/removed-101-4-from-unstable/">https://tracker.debian.org/news/1636301/removed-101-4-from-unstable/</a></p>
